## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e2ef6-486">下列範例示範如何使用這個屬性來指定重新導向 URL，當您在撰寫使用 HTTP 301 回應碼的永久重新導向程式碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e2ef6-486">The following example shows how to use this property to specify the redirect URL when you code a permanent redirect by using the HTTP 301 response code.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
Response.StatusCode = 301;  
Response.Status = "301 Moved Permanently";  
Response.RedirectLocation = "http://www.newurl.com ";  
Response.End();  
```
